<lb n="0640a10" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0640a11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0640a12" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1338</head><div1 type="other">
<lb n="0640a13" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0640003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】明本，此經麗本缺增上寺宋本缺</note>&CB00057;三首經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0640a14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0640a15" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0640004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（大）＋唐【元】</note><app n="0640004"><lem>唐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">大唐</rdg></app>三藏地婆訶羅奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0640a16" ed="T"/><mulu level="1" n="1" label="1 大輪金剛陀羅尼" type="其他"/><head>大輪金剛陀羅尼<note n="0640005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【元】</note><app n="0640005"><lem>一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">&lac;</rdg></app></head>
<lb n="0640a17" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0640a1701" type="dharani">訥謨薩怛唎耶　地毘迦喃　怛他揭多喃
<lb n="0640a18" ed="T"/>　唵毘囉　時毘囉時　摩訶斫迦囉　跋闍唎
<lb n="0640a19" ed="T"/>薩多薩多娑囉帝娑囉帝　怛唎曳怛唎曳毘
<lb n="0640a20" ed="T"/>陀末&CB00135;　三槃若&CB00135;　怛囉末底悉陀阿揭唎
<lb n="0640a21" ed="T"/>怛炎　娑婆訶</p>
<lb n="0640a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0640a2201">誦此陀羅尼三七遍即當入一切漫荼羅<note place="inline">壇也</note>
<lb n="0640a23" ed="T"/>所作皆成<note place="inline">誦&CB00057;。有身印手印。作印誦&CB00057;法即易成。若未入壇。不得&CB00364;作。今令誦此&CB00057;。即當入壇
<lb n="0640a24" ed="T"/>作印行不成盜法也</note>。</p></div1>
<lb n="0640a25" ed="T"/><div1 type="other"><mulu level="1" n="2" label="2 日光菩薩咒" type="其他"/><head>日光菩薩&CB00057;二</head>
<lb n="0640a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0640a2601" type="dharani">南謨勃陀瞿<note place="inline">上<note n="0640006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔聲〕－【元】下同</note><app n="0640006"><lem>聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>那<note place="inline">上聲</note>迷　南摩達摩　莫
<lb n="0640a27" ed="T"/>訶南謨僧伽多也泥底<note place="inline">丁以<note n="0640007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">切＝反【元】＊</note><app n="0640007"><lem>切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">反</rdg></app></note>哩部卑薩<note place="inline">僧沒<app source="0640007" type="＊"><lem>切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">反</rdg></app></note>咄
<lb n="0640a28" ed="T"/><note place="inline"><note n="0640008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（下）＋登【元】</note><app n="0640008"><lem>登</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">下登</rdg></app>沒<anchor id="fxT21p0640a02"/>反</note>擔<note place="inline">平聲</note>納摩</p>
<lb n="0640a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0640a2901"><note place="inline">誦此&CB00057;滅一切障亦能辟魔及除天災。又若誦一遍禮佛一拜。如此日別三時誦&CB00057;禮佛。未來當得二相端正具足果
<pb n="0640b" id="T21.1338.0640b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0640b01" ed="T"/>報</note>。</p></div1>
<lb n="0640b02" ed="T"/><div1 type="other"><mulu level="1" n="3" label="3 摩利支天咒" type="其他"/><head>摩利支天&CB00057;三</head>
<lb n="0640b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0640b0301" type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">上</note>摩利支曳　薩婆薩多婆頞陀利沙利娑
<lb n="0640b04" ed="T"/><note place="inline">上聲</note>婆<note place="inline">去聲</note>訶</p>
<lb n="0640b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0640b0501">誦此&CB00057;極護人身。當日別三時各誦一百八
<lb n="0640b06" ed="T"/>遍。</p>
<lb n="0640b07" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>&CB00057;三首經</jhead></juan></div1>
